snippet.title: Rose Bowl: Alabama Crimson Tide vs. Michigan Wolverines | Full Game Highlights | CFB Semifinal
snippet.description:
Check out these highlights from No. 1 Michigan's 27-20 OT win over No. 4 Alabama in the 2024 Rose Bowl matchup. The Wolverines will play the winner of the Sugar Bowl matchup between the Texas Longhorns and the Washington Huskies in the College Football National Championship.

snippet.title: Sugar Bowl: Texas Longhorns vs. Washington Huskies | Full Game Highlights
snippet.description:
Watch highlights from the Allstate Sugar Bowl where the Washington Huskies defeated the Texas Longhorns, 37-31. Michael Penix Jr. threw for 430 YDS & 2 TDS in the win, setting up a matchup vs. the Michigan Wolverines in the College Football Playoff Championship Game.
